ARGUMENT:: ele
elevation angle of beam direction in degree (-pi * 0.5 to pi * 0.5).

ARGUMENT:: int_float
0: "cardOrder" integer step from 0 (omni) up to "order".
1: float interpolation between "cardOrder" steps.

